{"tid":1531610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有位TVB演員影學生大頭","createTime":"2019-09-02T09:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T11:34:25.000Z","uid":148905,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1ba44022e5cfda3b8cbf9ecd27cd520439cc6ef0","tid":1531610,"uid":148905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:30:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chiuchiucherry/videos/3021282717913065?sfns=xmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchiuchiucherry%2Fvideos%2F3021282717913065%3Fsfns%3Dxmo&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR2%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=8ff25683\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chiuchiucherry/videos/3021282717913065?sfns=xmo</a><br />\n今日罷唔罷課係學生自由決定，關唔關你條八婆事。做咩連中學生都唔放過。不斷影相，拍片。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住睇下有邊位藍屍咁想出位。估唔到係TVB演員啵。我諗應該冇人會識。<br />\n不過我希望經過今日可以令更多人去認識你啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wzAoGOq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwzAoGOq.jpg&h=2fea6f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JBWrEDk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJBWrEDk.jpg&h=8320c7e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HpNKrjB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHpNKrjB.jpg&h=e1d840d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEOYvMh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEOYvMh.jpg&h=93205d33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qytJGSX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqytJGSX.jpg&h=bd6ee27e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M87VxZD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum